            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1664348032776-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>caramelised pineapple</strong> has cooled, chop it finely and return it to the bowl with the <strong>remaining pineapple juice</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the bowl with the <strong>remaining shallot </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1720708719560-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
