            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>remaining chopped coriander </strong>through the <strong>Caribbean-style pork</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Caribbean-style pork </strong>with the<strong> coconut rice </strong>and <strong>pineapple salsa </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
